      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "12 - TRELLIS TEXTURED  (single image -> textured 3D asset)\n\n1. Put your concept image (subject on plain or transparent background,\n   e.g. from workflow 01) in ComfyUI/input and pick it in the loader.\n2. Run. Output: output/3D/12_TRELLIS_TEXTURED_*.glb with UVs + baked texture.\n\nDefaults = the validated recipe: 200,000 faces, Xatlas unwrap, 2048 texture\n(~2 min on the 4080S). More detail: SimplifyMesh 500k-2M (slower to unwrap).\nSharper texture: texture_size 4096. Q5_K_M in LoadModel = a bit better, slower.\nFor a better mesh from 4 views, use 13_ASSET_FACTORY instead."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#432"
    }
